description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;There is opportunity for a Band 3 housekeeper to join the friendly team on Ward 2 YGC.&lt;/strong&gt; Successful applicants will need energy and drive in order to maintain the high standards demanded of this role. They will also have the ability to use their own initiative, have excellent communication skills and the ability to work within a team. The successful applicant will have excellent customer care skills, as a key function of the role is to support patients and relatives, to ensure a positive experience whilst they are a patient on the ward. It would be an advantage if they have recent experience of working in an acute health care setting. The successful applicant must a have a willingness to learn new skills and undertake further training if required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to speak Welsh is desirable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date:12/10/2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
